Package geodropSDKjava.dropOut

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JobsScheduledAction
    Action attribute of the JOB tag in the Jobs Scheduled request
    Report
    Gives information about the recipient's phone number
    SMSEstimatecost
    Request used to determine a higher estimate of the final cost of the message
    SMSEstimatecost_Response
    Response to a SMSEstimatecost request
    SMSJobsScheduled_Response
    Response to a SMSJobsScheduledStatus request, to a SMSJobsScheduledModify request and to a SMSJobsScheduledDelete request
    SMSJobsScheduledDelete
    Request used to delete a scheduled job
    SMSJobsScheduledModify
    Request used to modify a scheduled message, adding or removing recipients, changing its message text, its custom sender or its scheduled time
    SMSJobsScheduledStatus
    Request used to retrieve the overall status of a scheduled job
    SMSSend
    Request to send SMS messages specifying a text for the message, a list of recipients and a personalized sender
    SMSSend_Response
    Request to send SMS messages specifying a text for the message, a list of recipients and a personalized sender
    SMSStatus_Response
    Response to a SMSStatusJob request, to a SMSStatusAdhoc request and to a SMSStatusRange request
    SMSStatusAdhoc
    Request used to retrieve the status of any set of SMS messages
    SMSStatusJob
    Request used to get the overall status of a job
    SMSStatusRange
    Request used to retrieve the status of all SMS messages sent in a given time interval.
    StatusAdhocDest
    Uniquely identifies a single SMS message in the Geodrop archive
    StatusRequestType
    Used in the REQUEST_TYPE tag of the SMS Status request
